This file is not valid anymore. Visit the doc/html folder for current information.

All the OBM docs are in the doc folder.

This version of OBM is a developper only release as it should be difficult to
install and the datas and the database model are subject to change.


Licence
-------
OBM is protected by the GNU General Public License (See file COPYING).


Requirements
------------
OBM is developped under Linux (Kernel 2.0.36, glibc), Apache 1.3.3, PHP 3.0.5
and MySQL 3.22.8.
It should run whith any Apache 1.3.X (maybe with 1.2.X too), PHP 3.X and
MySQL 3.21.X or above. It has only been tested on Linux but it may run on
others UNIX where Apache, PHP and MySQL are available.

OBM currently only supports MySQL and PostgreSQL but others databases
support is planned.

Phplib (PHP Base Library) is used in OBM. Only parts needed by OBM are
present in this distribution, but Phplib can be obtain at phplib.shonline.de

Apache : www.apache.org
PHP    : www.php.net
MySQL  : www.mysql.org
Phplib : phplib.shonline.de
